tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,
review: i have never found a doctor like Dr rosy in my life.  i was so much anxious and in panic state in my first pregnancy. after going to many doctors , when i found her, i knew she was the one i am looking for. she is so friendly that never for a second i felt discomfort. i was so relieved after coming in contact with her. at every point she helped me on calls or texts no matter what time is . she cleared my all doubts and fears so calmly. in short i would say “ i am blessed to find a doctor like her in my pregnancy “

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Wait time,
review: She is very experienced and Sharp. My wife tested COVID positive in her 8th month of pregnancy. The way she treated her on every parameter after COVID damage was tremendous. I strongly recommend her. She is great at her profession but at the same time she is nice human being.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,
review:
Doctor Rosy Is very friendly with the patients and transparent in her treatment. She explains each and everything what we have to do, how we have to do and carefully listen the queries of the patient. Easily accessible on phone in emergency at any time. 
We are very thank full of Rosy mam for everything.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: Dr Rosy is very compassionate and she always listens to my worries patiently and takes time to make me understand about my treatment. Even during the days of lockdown, she was reachable over phone and she responded to all my questions without any delay . I would highly recommend Dr Rosy for all gynaecological issues .
Dr is very efficient, informed in detail about my health issues.  Satisfied with the consultation. Recommended to everyone.
